{"tid":1365397,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［整合］721 槍與子彈使用一覽","createTime":"2019-07-25T15:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T03:47:52.000Z","uid":189650,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4fcb436932cd05f5246b1d9c01e43ea55be9acb8","tid":1365397,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:31:05.000Z","msg":"警方公布7月21日用於清場的武器使用量:<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">55枚催淚彈與催淚煙<br />\n5發橡膠子彈<br />\n無布袋彈<br />\n24枚海綿彈</span><br />\n<br />\n撻撻撻連發的<span style=\"color: orange;\">胡椒彈</span><br />\n警方<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">沒有公佈</span></span>能連射的胡椒彈使用量<br />\n<br />\n7.21 警察開槍射胡椒彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/320505138857250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F320505138857250&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=c32e380d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/320505138857250</a><br />\n多發胡椒彈，0.09 有清楚射擊畫面<br />\n<br />\n721警方上環驅散示威者未有示警橋上開槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rzfz15is6pY&amp;t=0m55s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRzfz15is6pY%26t%3D0m55s&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=9bca2041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rzfz15is6pY&amp;t=0m55s</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》【引渡惡法】警4大防暴武器大晒冷 最恐怖係胡椒彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190612/59708607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190612%2F59708607&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=b6227e8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190612%2F59708607&h=46ab74e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190612/59708607</a><br />\n胡椒彈成分包括經特殊萃取的胡椒素，威力比一般催淚彈大。擊中人體後，子彈會爆開，釋出刺激性氣體，猶如中了胡椒噴霧，令吸入者呼吸道感到灼熱、流淚等，氣體更能穿透衣服接觸人體皮膚，造成身體不適與灼熱。被射中會有瘀傷印記，以便警方事後拘捕目標人物。<br />\n<br />\n雖然胡椒彈被視作非致命性武器，但根據使用指引，施發時需避免對準目標人物的臉部、喉嚨或脊骨，嚴重的可致命。外國過去更曾發生死亡案例，事發於2004年，美國波士頓警方為驅散上街慶祝的球迷人群，發射胡椒彈，不幸擊中一名傳理系學生Victoria Snelgrove的眼睛，使她大量出血，結果她在被射中12小時後不治，驗屍報告指胡椒彈在她眼後開出一個3/4吋的洞，損害了她的右腦，導致死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">催淚彈</span><br />\n催淚彈可分為<span style=\"color: orange;\">投擲式和槍發式</span>，其中投擲式可釋放較多氣體，施放範圍約15平方米，但內有23粒細彈頭，英國製造；而槍發式由<span style=\"color: orange;\">法德魯寸半口徑大口槍</span>發射 (取自《蘋果》)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">法德魯吋半口徑防暴槍</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pTWSxdB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpTWSxdB.jpg&h=9f4dd9d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《香港01》清場後遺未引爆催淚彈。（陳蕾蕾攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/43ExRip.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F43ExRip.jpg&h=9f9e268a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《香港01》【721遊行】西環衝突14人受傷一人嚴重 清場後遺未引爆催淚彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/354803/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F354803%2F&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=c6de32e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/354803/</a><br />\n<br />\n爆開後的催淚彈頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZTbDSGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZTbDSGY.jpg&h=a64980fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">橡膠子彈</span><br />\n警方使用橡膠子彈分為兩種，其中配以<span style=\"color: orange;\">法德魯防暴槍</span>發射的子彈內含3粒彈頭，由英國製造，有效射程是50至75米；而配以<span style=\"color: orange;\">雷明登霰彈槍</span>則可配最多8至9粒彈頭，由美國製造，有效射程是50至70米 (取自《蘋果》)<br />\n<br />\n(暫時因未找到7月21日橡膠子彈於地上的圖片)<br />\n於6月12日龍和道地上找到的橡膠子彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EtGoUU7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEtGoUU7.jpg&h=4a774fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/damon_pang/status/1138724387006361600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdamon_pang%2Fstatus%2F1138724387006361600&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=4392c2f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdamon_pang%2Fstatus%2F1138724387006361600&h=64a68fca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/damon_pang/status/1138724387006361600</a><br />\n<br />\nALS1202 Rubber Fin Rocket (Direct Fire)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.lesslethal.com/products/12-gauge/als1202-detail\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lesslethal.com%2Fproducts%2F12-gauge%2Fals1202-detail&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=7384ae82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.lesslethal.com/products/12-gauge/als1202-detail</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">雷明登霰彈槍</span><br />\n【721即時】 22:44 警察向示威者開槍。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/videos/336543320631999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcityusu.cbc%2Fvideos%2F336543320631999&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=7266ffc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/videos/336543320631999</a><br />\n<br />\n[有圖慎入] 橡膠彈可導致嚴重傷害或死亡<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cMuaeT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cMuaeT</a><br />\n在近距離內發射將導致嚴重傷害或死亡<br />\n因為該彈藥為低致死（Less-Lethal）<br />\n而不是非至死（Non-Lethal）<br />\n被擊中的部位很嚴重 組織被破壞 肉會凹進去 (by @乳細冇増)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">海綿彈</span><br />\n因此用<span style=\"color: orange;\">44MM發射器</span>發射海綿彈 (取自《RTHK》)<br />\n《RTHK》警方稱過去周日中上環共發射5發橡膠子彈24枚海綿彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470459-20190725.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470459-20190725.htm&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=08702d09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470459-20190725.htm&h=aa8fc735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470459-20190725.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/24/013502_0a36f7e994d24bc8b7209619084a4546.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F24%2F013502_0a36f7e994d24bc8b7209619084a4546.gif&h=1c31a724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方驅散干諾道西示威者 天橋上無預警下向人群開槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/inmediahk/videos/1307851056040490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Finmediahk%2Fvideos%2F1307851056040490&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=bcde2732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/inmediahk/videos/1307851056040490</a><br />\n2:07 開槍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/undergradnews/videos/2098323940469793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fundergradnews%2Fvideos%2F2098323940469793&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=1bfa2570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/undergradnews/videos/2098323940469793</a><br />\n1:40 裝填海綿彈<br />\n<br />\nALS4006D REACT Round (40MM)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.lesslethal.com/products/37mm-40mm/als4006d-detail\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lesslethal.com%2Fproducts%2F37mm-40mm%2Fals4006d-detail&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=9fc29d5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.lesslethal.com/products/37mm-40mm/als4006d-detail</a><br />\n<br />\n海綿彈即係40MM榴彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dqgevT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dqgevT</a><br />\n儘管比橡膠棍彈要軟，但在10m內擊中要害部位，仍然有致命的危險，而超過50m的距離基本上無效<br />\n<br />\n以國海綿子彈鎮暴 挨槍傷勢嚴重<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.pts.org.tw/article/330653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.pts.org.tw%2Farticle%2F330653&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hIDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=80008730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.pts.org.tw/article/330653</a><br />\n人權團體表示，以色列鎮暴警察兩年前改用海綿子彈以來，造成30多名巴勒斯坦人受傷，其中14人因此一眼失明。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n721 開槍時間與影片整理<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dpdKvT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dpdKvT</a><br />\n<br />\n知己知彼 百戰百勝圖解香港警察裝備<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cLKoBT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cLKoBT</a>"},{"pid":"55caf469fbda114260480b6dfa0c7c067f7e72c7","tid":1365397,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:33:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6390f5019842817faba49e09c695930defc9c9c8","tid":1365397,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6882a0b67448e19d32cdf635fe0e1e51e0824e0","tid":1365397,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf32fa091f54b57e2a40caa1e9abe9bccc9354e8","tid":1365397,"uid":209910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:37:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"885436200484f22356c2b9b12d956d44280ec0ba","tid":1365397,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22cdd88790969b435a3410b33e65df39dedff6c","tid":1365397,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl